title: Hello Friends
body:
So Violet is not doing well.  She got a shot that is making her better for a few days, but I know it will not last.  I am going to get her an MRI.  They suspect a brain lesion.  I have been sobbing a lot, but I will do what is best for her. 

Please send positive thoughts for my little Violet:)


How are you doing?  I hope you are doing great!  I haven’t decided if I’m going to do the Phandom Reverse Bang this round or not. Are you going to do it?

I talked to my side therapist yesterday and it was a bit weird because while she was sympathetic about Violet, she doesn’t get emotionally attached to animals.  That’s fine, but it is hard for me to understand.  I guess because I get SO emotionally attached.  She gets more attached to people, which I don’t, so I’m the weird one here, lol. 

I miss Dan.  Day 1 billion.


I am reading that the “technical difficulties” about Phil’s video is probably a merch delay, and that sounds about right.  I am loving his merch, btw.  So cool and subtle!  


Well, I hope you have a great day!  Hug your pet for me if you have one!


I’ll leave you with a little Gracie Allen.  Have an awesome day!
